(HORSE NEIGHING)

51:19.960 --> 51:22.839
Tell Simone to come see me. I
wanna apologize for yesterday.

51:26.680 --> 51:30.275
She left in a hurry
when you were took.

51:31.760 --> 51:33.273
Don't think
she's back yet.

51:34.920 --> 51:36.035
Hey.

51:36.840 --> 51:38.990
Sorry, missus,
but uh...

51:40.400 --> 51:41.515
What? What is it?

51:42.520 --> 51:46.479
