Supposed to talk to him directly.

51:47.280 --> 51:49.840
It's okay. We'll go
into the barn.

51:49.960 --> 51:52.679
No. No secrets here.

51:57.800 --> 51:59.234
Well, what is it, kid?
Spit it out.

52:01.120 --> 52:03.475
