(HORSE NEIGHING)

52:14.160 --> 52:15.833
I'm sorry.

52:22.520 --> 52:24.557
(O DEATH PLAYING)

52:25.800 --> 52:28.076
(SINGING) O, Death

52:29.640 --> 52:32.154
O, Death

52:33.600 --> 52:38.595
Won't you spare me
over till another year

52:39.760 --> 52:41.159
(KNOCK ON DOOR)

52:41.240 --> 52:43.231
MAN: Undertaker's
on his way up.

52:46.160 --> 52:49.835
Well, what is this
that I can't see

52:49.920 --> 52:54.630
With ice cold hands
takin' hold of me

52:57.080 --> 53:00.675
Well, I am death,
none can excel

53:00.760 --> 53:04.674
I'll open the door
to heaven or hell

53:05.600 --> 53:07.591
(ELEVATOR DOORS CLOSE)

53:08.800 --> 53:12.839
Whoa, death someone
would pray

53:12.960 --> 53:17.352
Could you wait to
call me another day

53:19.960 --> 53:23.476
The children prayed,
the preacher preached

53:23.560 --> 53:27.952
Time and mercy
is out of your reach

53:30.680 --> 53:34.514
I'll fix your feet
till you can't walk

53:34.600 --> 53:39.356
I'll lock your jaw
till you can't talk

53:41.600 --> 53:45.514
I'll close your eyes
SO you can't see

53:45.600 --> 53:50.117
This very hour,
come and go with me

53:53.280 --> 53:56.398
I am death
I come to take the soul

53:56.480 --> 54:00.997
Leave the body
and leave it cold

54:02.840 --> 54:05.309
Where's this eggplant who
can't stop shitting the bed?

54:08.680 --> 54:09.670
Gentlemen.

54:11.880 --> 54:13.917
(MAN EXCLAIMING)

54:18.240 --> 54:20.277
(BREATHING HEAVILY)

54:32.440 --> 54:34.238
Bag them and drop
them in the woods.

54:35.840 --> 54:37.638
We tell the boss
the Gerhardts got them.

54:41.160 --> 54:43.197
(RINGING)

55:12.760 --> 55:13.875
Hello?

55:14.080 --> 55:15.150
ED: Mike Milligan?

55:20.320 --> 55:21.390
Yes.

55:22.280 --> 55:23.839
Today's your lucky day.

55:25.680 --> 55:28.638
I've got Dodd Gerhardt in the
trunk of my car. You want him?

55:28.760 --> 55:30.751
(JUST DROPPED IN PLAYING)

55:54.640 --> 55:56.631
(SINGING)
I woke up this morning

55:56.760 --> 55:59.832
With the sundown shinin'in

56:02.600 --> 56:04.273
I found my mind

56:04.400 --> 56:07.552
In a brown paper bag within

56:10.560 --> 56:14.235
I tripped on a cloud
and fell eight miles high

56:14.480 --> 56:18.394
I tore my mind
on a jagged sky

56:18.520 --> 56:21.034
I just dropped in to see

56:21.120 --> 56:24.431
What condition my
condition was in

56:36.520 --> 56:39.990
I pushed my soul
in a deep dark hole

56:40.240 --> 56:42.038
And I followed it in

56:44.240 --> 56:47.631
I watched myself crawlin' out

56:47.720 --> 56:51.350
As I was a-crawlin'in

56:52.080 --> 56:55.960
I got up so tight
I couldn't unwind

56:56.040 --> 56:59.795
I saw so much
I broke my mind

57:00.040 --> 57:02.714
I just dropped in to see

57:02.800 --> 57:05.918
What condition my
condition was in
